  <h2>Probate Sales Are Complicated — We Help Simplify Them</h2>
  <p>Selling a property through probate involves court oversight, timelines, and coordination between heirs, attorneys, and title companies. We've worked through probate sales many times and understand how to fit into that process without adding stress.</p>

  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-box">
      <div class="icon">⚡</div>
